ent-RMCCoatWaistcoat = Жилетка
    .desc = Для какой-нибудь классной, убийственной забавы.
ent-RMCCoatSanitation = Служебная форма санитарных служб
    .desc = Униформа санитарных служб, используемая бригадами уборщиков в более процветающих колониях.
ent-RMCCoatParamedic = Спецодежда парамедиков
    .desc = Комплект красной спецодежды бригады парамедиков.
ent-RMCCoatParamedicGreen = { ent-RMCCoatParamedic }
    .desc = Комплект зелёной спецодежды бригады парамедиков.
ent-RMCBrownWEYACoat = brown WEYA coat
    .desc = A long, tough coat with the company logo on the back. Popular on colonies which require function over form.
ent-RMCWEYARainCoat = WEYA rain coat
    .desc = A bright, yellow raincoat with the Company logo. It's gaudy, sure, but it keeps the rain off well. Typically distributed to frontier colonies with heavy rain.
ent-RMCCoatSnow = Зимний костюм
    .desc = Стандартный зимний костюм, который защитит вас от холода и НЕ превратит в снежного человека
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivor = robust snow suit
    .desc = A snow suit. It can protect the wearer from extreme cold. This one seems to have been modified somewhat, and can both holster a gun and fit magazines.
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivorSecurity = security parka
    .desc = { ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivor.desc }
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivorCMBDeputy = CMB deputy parka
    .desc = A snow suit tailored to the CMB's needs. It can protect the wearer from extreme cold. The back is enscribed with the powerful letters of 'DEPUTY' representing justice, authority, and protection in the outer rim.
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivorNavy = navy parka
    .desc = { ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivor.desc }
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivorYellow = yellow parka
    .desc = { ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivor.desc }
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivorGreen = green parka
    .desc = { ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivor.desc }
ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivorPurple = purple parka
    .desc = { ent-RMCCoatSnowSurvivor.desc }
ent-RMCCoatSnowSoviet = soviet snowcoat
    .desc = A winter coat made in some desolate snowplanet. This wintercoat was made from the fur of local wildlife which donated their fur for the greater good of SPP!
ent-RMCCoatSnowLiaison = liaison's wintercoat
    .desc = A Weston-Yamada winter coat. Only the best comfort for the liaison in a cold environment.
